data.description: Range Pricing: Seller will counter accept offers between $370,000-$380,000. Seller will consider concessions for rate buy down or closing costs with favorable offer. Stunning 4-bed 2-bath home!  Inside you'll be greeted by an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining & kitchen areas. The spacious living room bathes in natural light creating an inviting atmosphere. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, elegant countertops & ample cabinet space. The primary bedroom is a true retreat with the bathroom featuring modern fixtures & a walk-in shower. The three additional bedrooms can be transformed to suit your needs - whether it's a home office, a cozy guest room, or a playroom.
